
Multi AZ:-
	DDB table is default Multi AZ replicated. Data redundantly copied to multiple AZ for Dyrability.

DDB Global Table:-
	Any DDB table by region specific and lie only in that region. but if you wants to replicate it in other rergion then you have to use the global table
	But for this first you have to enable the 'Stream' Once enabled then you can create the Global tabke in multiple region. 
	This are Multi Active table means you can READ and WRITE data in any of the table. This is not just read replica.
	Table remain in synch with each other and data copied among them.
	
	Data Conflict:-
		If a same data added or updated [data with same PK] tyhen the last one who updated will win.
